strings: <se_def>rice: I can honestly say that I feel so much better after a good night's sleep.
<se_def>rice: I sleep well in my own bed.
<se_def>rice: This maze is so much fun! I am so glad to be home!
<se_def>rice: Anyway, thanks to you, we got there safely. you owe me something
<se_high>breathe!: Yes, you saved our life. without you we are dying
<se_def>rice: But through our experiences together, we realized how important we are to each other. We have decided not to fight anymore.

<se_high>Carrie: No doubt that promise will last all of five minutes! But I'm sure we'll only fight like, y'know, normal brothers and sisters!<page>Carrie: Anyway, we want to give you some casino tokens as a reward.
<se_def>rice: A total of 600 people. Our casino opens in the morning. Visit us when you have time.
